1. heap is a complete binary tree.
  i) there will be all levels completely filled except the last level 
  ii)  at last level all  nodes  should be filled from left side
2. two types of heap 
   a) max heap -> parent node should be greater than or equal to a child node -> starting element here will be always greatest among all 
   b) min heap  -> parent node should be less than or equal to a child node
   
  
